@aparnacoronasafe I don't see value in removing these fields. These are Details Relavant to Public Health. It is good to hide these in a collapsible section, but should not be removed. These can be ignored for all Critical Care Patients. We could even consider having a selector (COVID/Non-COVID) Which would hide these. But I'm against removing them altogether.

Let's always choose to build a flexible system with more features, than a system with a very specialized set of features
